social_posts.post_text:
This EPIC human has been by my side, on tour across the us, night and day for the last 3 weeks straight

We have been working, playing, making music, sharing a car, meals, beds, laughter, insights, tears, and so so much more 

He has supported me in ways I can’t begin to explain, or find the words to express the depth of my gratitude

He has risen to meet every single challenge we have faced on the road and living the tour life

He’s shown up for me in a way no other man ever has

Played so many roles as my roadie, driver, therapist, hype man, reiki healer, music partner, and best friend

We have been in each others lives for years now and gone deep many times, but this last month has solidified our brotherhood like nothing else

My love and gratitude for him is beyond anything I could write or share here. I am blessed to not only have him in my life but to share in such deep connection and co-creation together 

Happy be-earth day @reiki.robert  This world is blessed to have you in it, and I am eternally grateful for you and your presence in my life!!

🪶💨❤️‍🔥

“Aloha FAMILY,

COME PLAY & PRAY WITH US!
 
The ILUMINA ceremonial immersion was created out of our intention and desire to share sacred space with you. To receive the deep healing, activation, and joy from bringing our beloved Utah community together.
 
 We have curated such a beautiful flow of offerings for you. We have brought together some of the most talented and epic humans that we know to share their gifts of medicine, music, and movement with you. 
 
We will begin by coming home to our beautiful body temples through breathwork with Lettie Crausby and a heart-opening yoga flow with Sadie Jane Sabin - fit for all skill levels. 
 
Once we are grounded and centered in our vessels, we will set our intentions to receive the healing & heart-expanding frequencies of ceremonial cacao medicine.  We work with a dear Mayan elder, Nana Marina, to source the most delicious & high vibrational cacao that has ever graced our lips. As the cacao melts into every cell, we will join Mountain Tribe to weave our songs of love to remember that our voices are stronger together, and to ignite the fires of our hearts!
 
 Once we have really fanned our inner flame, we will move all that beautiful energy through every inch of our body by dancing our prayers to the rhythms, beats, and melodies intentionally crafted by Shamanic Bass Artist, Light Language. When our ceremonial journey is coming to a close, we will be guided back home through a soundscape orchestrated by the one and only @reiki.robert 
 
We hope you will join us for an unforgettable evening.
And please do share this invitation with soul-aligned friends and family

Check the link in our Bio for tickets 🎟️

This Sunday’s show @clubhouseslc for @clubhouse.ecstatic.slc marks the LAST STOP on the west coast run of the LOTUS LEAVES TOUR

Falling on a powerful full moon in Sagittarius this one is set to be extra special 🌕

Wrapping up this leg of the tour is so surreal, it’s hard to believe that it’s already been 3 months and that I have traveled over 14,000 miles in just one quarter of a year ✨🔊

Life has shifted profoundly in such a short time, and the growth I have experienced as an artist and individual is mind blowing

I am truly grateful for everyone that has come out to pray and play with us along the way. The music and the medicine have been received so deeply. I am forever grateful for each and every one of you who has supported this project, connected and shared your homes, lives, and kind words about how the music resonates

HUGE MAHALOS to my agent @adamsaintsimons for making this all happen, and @reiki.robert for providing generous support along the way

The rest of the year is shaping up to be incredibly epic and I will be sharing new dates soon!

If you were along for the journey in any of the many cities we played in I would love to hear from you in the comments .. what were your favorite moments, songs, and experiences? ⬇️

📸 @exponential.visions
